comment: /**  * Returns the {@link Setting setting configuration} that is common for all caching realms  */
code: /**  * Returns the {@link Setting setting configuration} that is common for all caching realms  */ public static Set<Setting.AffixSetting<?>> getSettings(String type) {     return new HashSet<>(Arrays.asList(CACHE_HASH_ALGO_SETTING.apply(type), CACHE_TTL_SETTING.apply(type), CACHE_MAX_USERS_SETTING.apply(type), AUTHC_ENABLED_SETTING.apply(type))). }
